# API route conventions

- Use `export async function GET|POST|PUT|DELETE(...)` route handlers.
- Validate inputs at the boundary; return 400 on client mistakes.
- Return `Response.json(...)` for JSON responses.
- Do not leak internal error details to clients; log server-side if needed.
- Keep handlers thin; move logic into `src/lib/**` when it grows.

